{"tid":2098470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Food science一問","createTime":"2020-07-07T13:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T13:41:43.000Z","uid":297498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b79c382462419092bf48f8bf910bf99b1218637","tid":2098470,"uid":297498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"想問下大家<br />\n用Creaming method整Pound cake<br />\n如果用左豆腐代替蛋<br />\n點解會冇leavening effect 呢?<br />\n同埋點解會有煙韌嘅質地?<br />\n感激!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788a8d01bcdb0e05a3bc733563c1c700ff9071d4","tid":2098470,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"好簡單啫，因為你係用Creaming method整Pound cake吖麻，<br />\n因為你用左豆腐代替蛋，就會冇咗leavening effect。<br />\n另外，同樣道理，唔用食材有唔用化學反應，所以會有煙韌嘅質地。"}]}